Keys, who wore no makeup for the recent MTV Video Music Awards, has inspired local and international celebrities who have taken to social media au naturel.The 36-year-old Fallin' singer said she was tired of "the constant judgment of women" and felt "the strongest, most empowered, most free and most honestly beautiful that I have ever felt".The "naked face" has become the latest "must-have" among celebrities like Miley Cyrus, Kylie Jenner, Pearl Thusi, Kelly Khumalo and Samkelo Ndlovu.Ndlovu said: "My hair is natural and I go out in public bare-faced very often because I believe my body thrives in its natural form."